title: Sound & Stage Middle East - August 2014
description:
Sound & Stage Middle East - August 2014
 English | 52 Pages | True PDF | 23MB

Sound & Stage Middle East is the region's leading information resource for the professional audio-visual, lighting design and live staging production industries. 
Featuring a compelling mix of industry news, features, product showcases and technical installation profiles, Sound & Stage Middle East provides a comprehensive monthly round-up of the latest developments impacting these dynamic industry sectors. 

Sound & Stage Middle East aims to provide industry professionals with an insight into the latest technological developments and market trends set to impact the way they do business in the Middle East. 

The magazine is dedicated to ensuring the highest quality editorial content and providing the best possible news and information resource for key decision makers, along with technical analysis from experts in the field. 

Sound & Stage Middle East also acts as a market barometer and information resource for international firms looking to expand their presence in the region.
